00: 50 41 50 61 10 50 51 00

## Explain
MK-Pro compile report
Steps: 8/999999
Delivery: hex
Optimizer: exact maximum
Machine: mk61
Optimizer rules: automatic=yes; active=5, considered=0, candidates=48, planned=0
Budget: official=8, extra=0, physical=8
