  - dispatch@50/indirect-register-flow: 49 steps; rejected; selector is key-valued, not address-valued, and building an address register would not beat the compare-chain
  - dispatch@50/dark-indirect-table: 8 steps; considered; layout proof did not establish a conflict-free address/data table for this site
  - dispatch@50/super-dark-dispatch: 7 steps; considered; selector is key-valued, and layout proof did not place one-command cases at 48..53 with tails at 01..06

